The dragon hunt!
Young dragons have hatched in the remote mountains, kill them before they become a threat to all life in Gipath.
#subobj  1
Slay the first dragon
Find and kill the first green dragon. It is said that green dragons have been spotted among the lizards in the nearby forest.
#subobj  2
Slay the second dragon
Also take down the second green dragon from the sky!
#subobj  3
Slay the third dragon
A blue dragon was spotted among the lizards at the large lake. These lizards and the dragon are more dangerous than their counterparts.